    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>UIScrollBarのスクロール可能領域を指定するには、以下のように contentSizeプロパティを指定します。</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='objc'><span class='line'><span class="c1">//CGSizeMakeで横幅, 縦幅を指定する</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="n">self</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">scrollView</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">contentSize</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">CGSizeMake</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">320</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">568</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>
